{
  "_comment": "Default CircleMUD -> IronMUD shop mapping. Translates Circle ITEM_TYPE buy_types tokens (FOOD, LIQ CONTAINER, WEAPON, ...) into IronMUD ItemType strings used by shop_buys_types. Tokens with no IronMUD analogue surface as 'warn' (e.g. FIRE WEAPON, MISSILE — unimplemented in stock Circle). Edit to suppress noise (use 'drop') or add aliases. See docs/import-guide.md.",
